    "created_at": "2015-10-14T05:52:04Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-10-14T05:52:04Z",
    "body": "After a closer look, it's not easy to get rid of `DownloadItem` since the implementation of `SavePage` in Chromium has been hard-coded and integrated with `Download` related parts.\n\nBut we may handle this on Electron side, how about:\n\n```\nwin.webContents.savePage(`path/to/file.html`, 'HTMLOnly', function(download_item) {\n   download_item.on('done', function(state) {});\n});\n```\n"
  },
