    "created_at": "2015-10-14T06:05:29Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-10-14T06:05:29Z",
    "body": "Since we can get the `DownloadItem` of the `savePage`, we can probably add a custom user data to `DownloadItem` and make the `will-download` event ignore such items, and then call the callback of `savePage` when the `done` event of `DownloadItem` is called.\n\nThis makes the implementation much more complicated, but a decent API should worth the efforts.\n"
  },
